00:33:32.650 --> 00:33:36.020
HENRY FAULKNER: OK, in terms
of sort of the audience here

00:33:36.020 --> 00:33:38.080
at Google and a lot of
technologists and people

00:33:38.080 --> 00:33:42.580
who create tools, how do
