00:33:42.580 --> 00:33:46.090
do to make technology
foster relationships

00:33:46.090 --> 00:33:50.540
rather than be something
that divides us?

00:33:50.540 --> 00:33:52.028
MICHAEL JASCZ: I'm not sure.

00:33:52.028 --> 00:33:53.360
[LAUGHTER]

00:33:53.360 --> 00:33:56.855
Technology has saved
lives in many ways.

00:33:59.620 --> 00:34:05.380
I find it hard to read
